title: Efficiency for rent -$675.00
posting_body: ['Efficiency for rent.', 'Single occupancy only.', 'All utilities are included in the rent, with the exception of cable and Wi-Fi.', 'Unit is privately owned and has had the same owner since 1983.', 'This efficiency is located near Hamline College.', 'It has private bath/shower.', 'There is no cooking in this unit, as there is no stove.', 'Though a microwave, crockpot, coffee pot, etc can be used.', 'It does have a small, camper sized refrigerator.', 'No pets and no smoking allowed in this unit.', 'This apartment building is safe, with a locked main entry.', 'This building is also very quiet, very clean, and well maintained.', 'Unit is small about the size of a large bedroom.', 'One year lease requested.', 'Central air, off street parking, close to the bus line.', 'Laundry facilities on site.']
